WEBVTT

00:00.338 --> 00:02.344
Previously on
<i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:02.369 --> 00:04.075
Are you saying there's
a government in Charleston?

00:04.101 --> 00:06.695
Elected by almost 3,000
civilians in the new capital.

00:06.720 --> 00:08.256
We need to get back
in the war.

00:08.281 --> 00:10.767
Seems like Charleston might be
a good place to do that.

00:10.809 --> 00:12.007
You still in love
with her?

00:12.032 --> 00:13.705
No. Of course not.

00:14.693 --> 00:17.263
I know exactly what you'll do to
these people if you get the chance.

00:17.311 --> 00:19.169
Just gonna take off
without saying goodbye?

00:19.326 --> 00:21.093
When that Overlord
invaded my mind,

00:21.118 --> 00:22.969
he couldn't keep his thoughts
completely walled off.

00:23.220 --> 00:24.821
Come after me,
again and again.

00:24.846 --> 00:26.201
We're gonna keep rolling

00:26.226 --> 00:27.946
all the way to Charleston!

00:27.971 --> 00:29.207
This is the final push.

